data.description: Nestled in the coveted Bixby Knolls neighborhood of Long Beach, this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo epitomizes modern comfort and convenience. Located on the top floor, the unit boasts a stylishly updated kitchen featuring quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a charming sliding barn door pantry. The space is bathed in natural light, enhanced by recessed lighting and fresh paint, while vaulted ceilings lend an airy elegance. Step onto the balcony to enjoy peaceful courtyard views. Two off-street parking spots add to the ease of living here. Plus, the condo complex offers on-site laundry, a community pool, a spa, and a BBQ area, providing a resort-like lifestyle. With dining, entertainment, and shopping options just moments away, this condo is your gateway to the vibrant Bixby Knolls lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your own.
